data.description: A rare opportunity arises in the serene community of South Gulf Cove, where the Florida Suncoast lifestyle meets its zenith. Nestled on an expansive, double tip lot spanning nearly one acre, this exquisite residence, custom-built by Roberts Homes, boasts an unrivaled 400 feet of water frontage, embracing the convergence of the Antwerp and Viscount waterways. Impossibility to replicate this idyllic haven makes it a truly unique gem. Meticulously maintained, and recently renovated, this architectural masterpiece welcomes you with a grand entrance that instantly captivates your senses with awe-inspiring water views. Step onto the covered lanai, and a vision of tranquil luxury unfolds. Picture yourself basking by the pristine pool or unwinding in the spa, lulled by the gentle sway of palm trees in the breeze as boats glide by. As the sun sets, descend to your private dock, complete with a 9,000lb lift, and embark on a picturesque sunset cruise. Indoors, the opulence continues. Sixteen-foot, vaulted ceilings grace the main living areas, exuding an air of grandeur. The Owner's suite showcases a spacious bedroom with mesmerizing pool and water views, dual walk-in closets, and a luxurious bathroom equipped with a soaking tub, walk-in shower, and separate vanities. What sets this home apart are the RECENT UPGRADES that add even more value to this remarkable property: a NEW GRANITE OVER STEEL ROOF in 2023 with a 50-year warranty, a new Clearview pool screen enclosure, all new kitchen appliances, new quartz kitchen countertops, and all new light fixtures and ceiling fans throughout the interior and exterior. Additionally, a 3 Zone HVAC system was installed in 2021, along with a new landscaping and irrigation system. Your culinary haven awaits in the well-appointed kitchen, offering abundant cabinetry and countertop space, a double oven, cooktop, and a walk-in pantry. Two guest bedrooms with a convenient Jack and Jill bath, a versatile den that can serve as a 4th bedroom, generously sized family and laundry rooms, and elegant formal living and dining areas complete the interior space. The three-car garage boasts added conveniences, including a separate workshop/office and dance studio with ballet bar, making it the ideal space for the hobbyist or entrepreneur. South Gulf Cove's prime location ensures easy access to shopping, dining, golfing, marinas, and pristine beaches, all just minutes away. Seize this extraordinary opportunity to embrace the Florida Suncoast lifestyle that you have always dreamed of! Don't miss out on this incredible offering. Contact us today to explore this one-of-a-kind home!
